Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用亞空間航法到地表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太大膽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我你從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20世紀中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類發現宇宙是由波動而生是移動著的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2046年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類發現人體發出的某種波動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可變換成強力的宇宙能源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個波動在人感動時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起重要的人的時候會增強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之人在專注唱歌時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會產生巨大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類因此將這未知的力量稱為歌能源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭為什不回頭看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼生氣幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌靠的是心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對手不是人我很難進入狀況的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們的敵人也不是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌對他們行不行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看花有沒有反應就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧我會讓這些向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起回頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 是時空異常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼歌能源探測器會發出這樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人完全沒有動嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛我只是差你一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵對那聲音產生反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵動了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔這個借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等你想去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了就馬上給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你打的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想來搶走我們的礦石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔心我搶你們挖的東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我對那個沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要開槍了你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼他想打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個很舊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手不准你碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿是灰塵的銀色吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別驚慌這裡很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他一吼肯定又要發生不祥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於有懂事的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安  BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 我的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想挖的巴魯納吉姆礦石  可能已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都挖了20年了挖到的全是些化石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡以前都是綠地是個暖和的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的以前2000年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是詛咒之聲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從開始有那個以後就事件不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球有怪物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼蓋爾爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰敢唱!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢作怪的話 我不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子在這星球出生後一直沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從他的父親死後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就迷上銀河網路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他爺爺討厭音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他喜歡音樂的程度不下於他父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫恰恰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說那個吉他是恰恰的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人隨時可能攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:10:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉卻一點自覺也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實很傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過巴薩拉是有野性直覺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那神祕的聲音說不定真有什麼祕密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他的野性直覺令人困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他應該稍微有點理性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 各位 要亞空間航行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大雪 吠叫 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸死掉的詛咒之山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知你爸為何死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不是它害的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是它害的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒感覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我的種子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,種子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,種子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的種子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰在冰中找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的種子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電視
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是電視
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是歌能源探測器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒魔怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞到你的心啦?這不是詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可不是泛泛之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞人心...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該在這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是從時空的扭曲 計算出來的座標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點誤差但是也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以巴薩拉的個性遲早會唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能 是上次那個聲音先傳出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反應點呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個星球的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就有找等於沒找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相當的混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視野太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不見 看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多羅 坐穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那個打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 不能太勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那個打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流浪的.....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流浪的傑特拉帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是流浪的傑特拉帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是他發出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 雷伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲能源探測器 好像\N無法承受能源的急速變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能在做歌唱大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 查出地點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該在那顆星球的反面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是應該?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER.....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要坐 BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能讓你坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在起要來真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的歌吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱的好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小的人類有這麼大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾NSP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感測到異常的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾NSP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感測到異常的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢之火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 蓋佩爾尼奇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  我知道夢之火焰的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是不合我的夢的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把他抹殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,納塔尼巴爾肯已調整完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去測試性能吧 是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟格拉比爾一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候看過林明美的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是很怪的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小人類女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用歌聲阻止了  我們傑特拉帝人的大艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問爸媽這不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們卻說是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有林明美這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是我想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對要成為不輸給林明美的厲害歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是你就到這裡練歌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人多的城市  無法大聲唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡對著雪山  做發聲練習罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是件好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過銀河很大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為自己練得很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻遇上你這樣的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌是沒有勝負的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌聲非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直撞你的心?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你也直撞我的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好巨大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普羅多戴比爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普羅多戴比爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 是很強的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了你要乖乖躲在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.39,0:24:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是異常靈魂的真面目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死它 它一點也不美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:24:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打死你!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.79,0:25:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然之美  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛彈太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是為了這種事修行的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.47,0:25:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.71,0:25:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.61,0:25:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種靈魂...怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好響亮阿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.50,0:25:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然用歌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的只用歌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我也要上去 FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.67,0:25:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我也要上去FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER  我也要上去FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.64,0:26:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這種事!? 這就是歌的力量嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.51,0:26:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這種事!? 這就是歌的力量嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.02,0:26:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多羅
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.49,0:26:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲波對那傢伙行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.46,0:26:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波長已經調整過
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的改造美
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.41,0:26:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.30,0:26:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得已使用禁忌絕招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.60,0:26:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合體
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.25,0:27:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三合一
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.15,0:27:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你們無法使用歌打倒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.22,0:27:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.36,0:27:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.54,0:27:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.07,0:27:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了 洪水來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.01,0:27:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大洪水
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.31,0:27:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自詛咒之山
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.75,0:27:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多羅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.09,0:27:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過 聲波不再有效果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.20,0:28:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.90,0:28:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼蓋爾爺爺你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.57,0:28:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我死也不走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.04,0:28:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別固執了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.38,0:28:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛 瑪露卡麗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.01,0:28:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要等到佩多羅回來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.55,0:28:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.21,0:28:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.08,0:28:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.11,0:28:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米蓮?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:28:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米蓮  設定打開聲音擴大器
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.92,0:29:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.19,0:29:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.06,0:29:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.54,0:29:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.91,0:29:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 我快裂開了!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.16,0:29:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差異太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.13,0:29:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.77,0:29:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行三合一的限制到了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.34,0:29:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 用突擊之美
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.65,0:30:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要撞上山了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.79,0:30:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要撞上去  這是引退之美
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.15,0:30:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛米莉亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.19,0:30:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.50,0:30:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛米莉亞 愛米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.44,0:30:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛米莉亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.74,0:30:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.48,0:31:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧? 愛米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.02,0:31:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是喝了點水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.92,0:31:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻  太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.09,0:31:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌的力量好厲害唷
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.99,0:31:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.96,0:31:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過...其實
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.03,0:31:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想把自己的心  也傳給他們懂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.27,0:31:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.04,0:31:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,種子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.04,0:31:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的種子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.44,0:31:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩多羅
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.81,0:31:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰的種子 看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.51,0:31:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.95,0:31:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信 埋在冰理兩千的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.85,0:31:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀河宇宙種子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.72,0:31:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發芽了!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.52,0:31:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估計是歌的力量造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.56,0:31:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.56,0:31:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌有那種力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.76,0:31:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.50,0:31:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:31:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 米蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.47,0:32:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.37,0:32:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.43,0:32:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.63,0:32:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的歌太難懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,紫色的全景畫 銀河的高速路 默默注視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,便能 敲擊我的心房 SHOOTING STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不夜之城 與我不斷加速的心跳重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾向著未知的明天祈禱之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所聽到的 那動聽旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可思議的歌聲將我緊緊擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,請告訴我 SEVENTH MOON 這心中的迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,將會引領我去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼藍搖曳的 SEVENTH MOON 在迴盪的旋律之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有沉醉於舞步 去不斷尋找答案一途
